Subject: drm/i915/display: Wait at least 2 frames before selective update
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: ce0eacbbd922b91ce28523b167ef848d0f76f908
